comments: Lively II (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in White's (CHI) path and the contact is marginal as he moves towards the basket.
Lively II (DAL) braces for the ensuing contact with Vucevic (CHI) during his post shot attempt.
Williams (DAL) and DeRozan (CHI) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.
Caruso (CHI) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.

Vucevic (CHI) jumps vertically contesting the driving shot attempt by Hardy (DAL) and the contact is created by Hardy extending his left elbow into Vucevic.  As Vucevic retracts his right arm towards his own body, he grazes Hardy's left arm but the contact is marginal.
White (CHI) reaches for the loose ball and extends his leg backwards and incidental contact occurs with Green (DAL) that results in both players losing their balance.
Lively II (DAL) blocks the shot attempt by White (CHI) after it reaches its apex and is on its downward flight towards the basket.
Doncic (DAL) and Caruso (CHI) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
White (CHI) is not in a position in Jones Jr.'s (DAL) path, but the resulting contact to Jones Jr.'s side is marginal as he makes the pass.
White (CHI) commits a take foul on Williams (DAL).
Vucevic (CHI) and Jones Jr. (DAL) come together as Jones Jr. attempts to move underneath him and the resulting contact is marginal.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul on Lively II (DAL).
